    <title>ROS常用命令</title>
    <url>/2022/04/29/ROS%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="ROS文件系统导览"><a href="#ROS文件系统导览" class="headerlink" title="ROS文件系统导览"></a>ROS文件系统导览</h1><h2 id="rospack命令"><a href="#rospack命令" class="headerlink" title="rospack命令"></a>rospack命令</h2><ul>
<li><strong>简介：</strong><a href="http://wiki.ros.org/rospack">rospack</a>允许你获取软件包的有关信息。在本教程中，我们只涉及到<code>find</code>参数选项，该选项可以返回软件包的所在路径。</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 用法：</span></span><br><span class="line">rospack find [package_name]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 范例：</span></span><br><span class="line">rospack find roscpp</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 输出：</span></span><br><span class="line">YOUR_INSTALL_PATH/share/roscpp</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 如果你是在Ubuntu操作系统上通过`apt`安装的ROS，你看到的应该是：</span></span><br><span class="line">/opt/ros/&lt;distro&gt;/share/roscpp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="roscd命令"><a href="#roscd命令" class="headerlink" title="roscd命令"></a>roscd命令</h2><ul>
<li><strong>简介：</strong><a href="http://wiki.ros.org/rosbash#roscd">roscd</a>是<a href="http://wiki.ros.org/rosbash">rosbash</a>命令集的一部分，它允许你直接切换目录（<a href="http://ss64.com/bash/cd.html">cd</a>）到某个软件包或者软件包集当中。</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="常规"><a href="#常规" class="headerlink" title="常规"></a>常规</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 用法：</span></span><br><span class="line">roscd [locationname[/subdir]]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 范例</span></span><br><span class="line">roscd roscpp  <span class="comment"># 要想验证是否能切换到roscpp包的位置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">pwd</span>           <span class="comment"># 当前工作目录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 你应该会看到：</span></span><br><span class="line">YOUR_INSTALL_PATH/share/roscpp</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 你可以看到`YOUR_INSTALL_PATH/share/roscpp`和之前使用`rospack find`输出的路径是一样的。</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 进入存储ROS日志文件的目录。需要注意的是，如果你没有执行过任何ROS程序，系统会报错说该目录不存在。</span></span><br><span class="line">roscd <span class="built_in">log</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>其他知识：</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>注意：就像ROS中的其它工具一样，<a href="http://wiki.ros.org/roscd">roscd</a>只能切换到那些路径已经包含在<a href="http://wiki.ros.org/ROS/EnvironmentVariables#ROS_PACKAGE_PATH">ROS_PACKAGE_PATH</a>环境变量中的软件包。要查看 <a href="http://wiki.ros.org/ROS/EnvironmentVariables#ROS_PACKAGE_PATH">ROS_PACKAGE_PATH</a>中包含的路径，可以输入：</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="variable">$ROS_PACKAGE_PATH</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>你的<a href="http://wiki.ros.org/ROS/EnvironmentVariables#ROS_PACKAGE_PATH">ROS_PACKAGE_PATH</a>环境变量应该包含那些保存有ROS软件包的路径，并且每个路径之间用冒号（:）分隔开来。一个典型的<a href="http://wiki.ros.org/ROS/EnvironmentVariables#ROS_PACKAGE_PATH">ROS_PACKAGE_PATH</a>环境变量如下：</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/opt/ros/&lt;distro&gt;/base/install/share</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>跟其他环境变量路径类似，你可以在<a href="http://wiki.ros.org/ROS/EnvironmentVariables#ROS_PACKAGE_PATH">ROS_PACKAGE_PATH</a>中添加更多的目录，每条路径使用冒号（:）分隔。</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="进入子目录"><a href="#进入子目录" class="headerlink" title="进入子目录"></a>进入子目录</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">roscd roscpp/cmake     <span class="comment"># 切换到一个软件包或软件包集的子目录中。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">pwd</span>                    <span class="comment"># 显示工作目录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 你应该会看到：</span></span><br><span class="line">YOUR_INSTALL_PATH/share/roscpp/cmake</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="rosls命令"><a href="#rosls命令" class="headerlink" title="rosls命令"></a>rosls命令</h2><p><strong>简介：</strong><a href="http://wiki.ros.org/rosbash#rosls">rosls</a> 是<a href="http://wiki.ros.org/rosbash">rosbash</a>命令集的一部分，它允许你直接按软件包的名称执行 <a href="http://ss64.com/bash/ls.html">ls</a> 命令（而不必输入绝对路径）。显示指定软件包中的文件列表。</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 用法：</span></span><br><span class="line">rosls [locationname[/subdir]]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 范例：</span></span><br><span class="line">rosls roscpp_tutorials</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 输出：</span></span><br><span class="line">cmake launch package.xml  srv</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="ROS节点"><a href="#ROS节点" class="headerlink" title="ROS节点"></a>ROS节点</h1><h2 id="rosnode命令"><a href="#rosnode命令" class="headerlink" title="rosnode命令"></a>rosnode命令</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rosnode list                  <span class="comment"># 显示当前正在运行的ROS节点信息</span></span><br><span class="line">rosnode info [node_name]      <span class="comment"># 返回某个节点中的topic信息。</span></span><br><span class="line">rosnode ping my_turtle        <span class="comment"># 测试节点是否正常</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="rosrun命令"><a href="#rosrun命令" class="headerlink" title="rosrun命令"></a>rosrun命令</h2><p><strong>简介：</strong><code>rosrun</code>可以让你用包名直接运行软件包内的节点（而不需要知道包的路径）</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 用法</span></span><br><span class="line">rosrun [package_name] [node_name]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 重新为节点分配名称</span></span><br><span class="line">rosrun  turtlesim  turtlesim_node   __name:=my_turtle</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="rostopic命令"><a href="#rostopic命令" class="headerlink" title="rostopic命令"></a>rostopic命令</h1><p><strong>简介：</strong>节点之间通过话题（topic）通信</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rostopic bw [topic_name]    <span class="comment"># 显示话题使用的带宽</span></span><br><span class="line">rostopic delay [topic_name] <span class="comment"># 显示标题中时间戳的话题延迟</span></span><br><span class="line">rostopic <span class="built_in">echo</span> [topic_name]  <span class="comment"># 将消息打印到屏幕</span></span><br><span class="line">rostopic find [topic_name]  <span class="comment"># 按类型查找话题</span></span><br><span class="line">rostopic hz [topic_name]    <span class="comment"># 显示话题的发布率</span></span><br><span class="line">rostopic info [topic_name]  <span class="comment"># 打印关于活动话题的信息</span></span><br><span class="line">rostopic list               <span class="comment"># 列出活跃话题</span></span><br><span class="line">rostopic pub                <span class="comment"># 将数据发布到话题</span></span><br><span class="line">rostopic <span class="built_in">type</span> [topic_name]  <span class="comment"># 打印话题或字段类型</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="ROS服务"><a href="#ROS服务" class="headerlink" title="ROS服务"></a>ROS服务</h1><h2 id="rosservice命令"><a href="#rosservice命令" class="headerlink" title="rosservice命令"></a>rosservice命令</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rosservice list         <span class="comment"># 输出活跃服务的信息</span></span><br><span class="line">rosservice call         <span class="comment"># 用给定的参数调用服务</span></span><br><span class="line">rosservice <span class="built_in">type</span>         <span class="comment"># 输出服务的类型</span></span><br><span class="line">rosservice find         <span class="comment"># 按服务的类型查找服务</span></span><br><span class="line">rosservice uri          <span class="comment"># 输出服务的ROSRPC uri</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="rosparam命令"><a href="#rosparam命令" class="headerlink" title="rosparam命令"></a>rosparam命令</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rosparam list                         <span class="comment"># 查看参数服务器上的参数</span></span><br><span class="line">rosparam <span class="built_in">set</span> [param_name]             <span class="comment"># 设置参数值</span></span><br><span class="line">rosparam get [param_name]             <span class="comment"># 读取参数值</span></span><br><span class="line">rosservice call /clear                <span class="comment"># 使得参数的修改能生效</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">rosparam dump [file_name] [namespace] <span class="comment"># 将参数写入文件中</span></span><br><span class="line">rosparam load [file_name] [namespace] <span class="comment"># 从文件中读取参数</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 范例：</span></span><br><span class="line">rosparam dump params.yaml             <span class="comment"># 将参数写入params.yaml文件：</span></span><br><span class="line">rosparam load params.yaml copy_turtle <span class="comment"># 将yaml文件重载入新的命名空间，例如copy_turtle：</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h1 id="rqt相关命令"><a href="#rqt相关命令" class="headerlink" title="rqt相关命令"></a>rqt相关命令</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rqt                            <span class="comment"># rqt集成显示器</span></span><br><span class="line">rqt_bag [bag_file]             <span class="comment"># bag包查看器</span></span><br><span class="line">rqt_graph                      <span class="comment"># 查看节点、话题之间的连接关系</span></span><br><span class="line">rqt_plot                       <span class="comment"># 用于绘制曲线</span></span><br><span class="line">rqt_console                    <span class="comment"># 连接到ROS的日志框架，显示节点的输出信息</span></span><br><span class="line">rqt_logger_level               <span class="comment"># 改变日志的级别Debug|Info|Warn|Error|Fatal</span></span><br><span class="line">rqt_image_view                 <span class="comment"># 图像查看器</span></span><br><span class="line">rqt_dep                        <span class="comment"># 功能包的依赖关系图</span></span><br><span class="line">rqt_shell                      <span class="comment"># 提供交互式shell的Python GUI插件</span></span><br><span class="line">rosrun rqt_tf_tree rqt_tf_tree <span class="comment"># 查看tf树</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="rosmsg命令"><a href="#rosmsg命令" class="headerlink" title="rosmsg命令"></a>rosmsg命令</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rosmsg show        <span class="comment"># 显示消息类型及参数描述</span></span><br><span class="line">rosmsg info        <span class="comment"># 显示消息信息</span></span><br><span class="line">rosmsg list        <span class="comment"># 列出所有消息</span></span><br><span class="line">rosmsg md5         <span class="comment"># 显示md5加密后的消息</span></span><br><span class="line">rosmsg package     <span class="comment"># 显示某个功能包下的所有消息</span></span><br><span class="line">rosmsg packages    <span class="comment"># 列出包含消息的功能包</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="rosbag相关命令"><a href="#rosbag相关命令" class="headerlink" title="rosbag相关命令"></a>rosbag相关命令</h1><h2 id="rosbag-record"><a href="#rosbag-record" class="headerlink" title="rosbag record"></a>rosbag record</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rosbag record [/topic_name] <span class="comment"># 录制bag包，可同时指定多个话题名</span></span><br><span class="line">	-a, -all                    <span class="comment"># 录制所有话题</span></span><br><span class="line">	-e, -regex                  <span class="comment"># 使用正则表达式指定话题名</span></span><br><span class="line">	-O [bag_file]               <span class="comment"># （大写）为录制的包重命名为[bag_file]</span></span><br><span class="line">	-o [prefix]                 <span class="comment"># （小写）为数据包加前缀</span></span><br><span class="line">	-d, -duration 10            <span class="comment"># 延时10秒播放</span></span><br><span class="line">	-u 10                       <span class="comment"># 仅播放前10秒</span></span><br><span class="line">    -l 1000                     <span class="comment"># 录制该主题1000个消息限制</span></span><br><span class="line">	--duration=30               <span class="comment"># 持续30s录制，还可以指定m,h，和--split类似</span></span><br><span class="line">	–node=[NODE_name]           <span class="comment"># 录制给定节点下的所有话题</span></span><br><span class="line">	--<span class="built_in">split</span>						<span class="comment"># 分文件存储</span></span><br><span class="line">		--size=1024                 <span class="comment">#空间达到1024M后分文件存储</span></span><br><span class="line">		--duration=30               <span class="comment">#持续时间到30s后分文件存储</span></span><br><span class="line">		--duration=5m               <span class="comment">#持续时间到5m后分文件存储</span></span><br><span class="line">		--duration=2h               <span class="comment">#持续时间到2h后分文件存储</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="rosbag-play"><a href="#rosbag-play" class="headerlink" title="rosbag play"></a>rosbag play</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rosbag play [bag_file]       <span class="comment"># 播放bag包</span></span><br><span class="line">	-r 0.5,--rate=0.5           <span class="comment"># 播放0.5倍速率</span></span><br><span class="line">	-l, --loop                  <span class="comment"># 循环播放</span></span><br><span class="line">	-s 10, --start=10           <span class="comment"># 从第10秒开始播放</span></span><br><span class="line">	-d 10, --delay=10           <span class="comment"># 延时10秒播放</span></span><br><span class="line">	-u 10, --duration=10        <span class="comment"># 仅播放前10秒</span></span><br><span class="line">	-q, -quiet                  <span class="comment"># 播放不显示log</span></span><br><span class="line">	-i, -immediate              <span class="comment"># 立即播放包，没有等待</span></span><br><span class="line">	--queue=SIZE                <span class="comment"># 使用大小为 SIZE 的传出队列（默认为 100）</span></span><br><span class="line">	--clock --hz                <span class="comment"># 发布时钟时间，并指定/clock的时钟频率为200hz          </span></span><br><span class="line">	--pause                     <span class="comment"># 开始播放立刻暂停，按空格继续</span></span><br><span class="line">	--topic [/topic_name]       <span class="comment"># 只播放单个话题</span></span><br><span class="line">	--topics [/topic_name] ...  <span class="comment"># 播放多个话题</span></span><br><span class="line">	--pause-topics              <span class="comment"># （黑名单模式）播放期间暂停的主题</span></span><br><span class="line">	--skip-empty=SEC            <span class="comment"># 跳过包中没有消息超过 SEC 秒的区域</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="rosbag-info"><a href="#rosbag-info" class="headerlink" title="rosbag info"></a>rosbag info</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rosbag info [bag_file]           <span class="comment"># 显示bag包的详细信息</span></span><br><span class="line">	-y, --yaml                   <span class="comment"># 以yaml形式显示话题信息</span></span><br><span class="line">	--freq                       <span class="comment"># 以频率形式显示包中的话题信息</span></span><br><span class="line">	-k KEY, --key=KEY            <span class="comment"># 打印给定键的信息</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="rosbag-filter"><a href="#rosbag-filter" class="headerlink" title="rosbag filter"></a>rosbag filter</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rosbag filter [options] INBAG OUTBAG EXPRESSION <span class="comment"># 按照规则截取部分bag包</span></span><br><span class="line">EXPRESSION：</span><br><span class="line"> * topic: 话题名</span><br><span class="line"> * m: 消息类型名（不会用）</span><br><span class="line"> * t: 消息时间 (t.secs, t.nsecs)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 范例</span></span><br><span class="line">rosbag filter input.bag output.bag <span class="string">&quot;(topic == &#x27;/chinook/ouster/points&#x27; or topic ==&#x27;/visensor/imu&#x27; or topic == &#x27;/visensor/left/image_raw&#x27;) and (t.to_sec() &gt;= 1566248111.46 and t.to_sec() &lt;= 1566248161.46)&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="rosbag修复"><a href="#rosbag修复" class="headerlink" title="rosbag修复"></a>rosbag修复</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rosbag reindex xxx.bag.active</span><br><span class="line">rosbag fix xxx.bag.active result.bag</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="rosbag中pcd提取"><a href="#rosbag中pcd提取" class="headerlink" title="rosbag中pcd提取"></a>rosbag中pcd提取</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rosrun pcl_ros bag_to_pcd tunnel5.bag /robot/dlo/map_node/map pcd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="其他"><a href="#其他" class="headerlink" title="其他"></a>其他</h1><h2 id="rviz-为话题提供正确的fixed-frame"><a href="#rviz-为话题提供正确的fixed-frame" class="headerlink" title="rviz 为话题提供正确的fixed frame"></a>rviz 为话题提供正确的fixed frame</h2><ul>
<li>方法一：使用rostopic</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rostopic <span class="built_in">echo</span> /velodyne/points | grep frame_id <span class="comment"># 显示7行grep -a7</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>方法二：使用rqt_bag</li>
</ul>
<p>使用rqt_bag查看bag包中的raw data，找到header中的frame_id</p>
<h2 id="激光雷达中激光数据类型datatype与数字的对应关系"><a href="#激光雷达中激光数据类型datatype与数字的对应关系" class="headerlink" title="激光雷达中激光数据类型datatype与数字的对应关系"></a>激光雷达中激光数据类型datatype与数字的对应关系</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># PointCloud2 消息格式保存一个点条目的描述。</span></span><br><span class="line">uint8 INT8    = 1</span><br><span class="line">uint8 UINT8   = 2</span><br><span class="line">uint8 INT16   = 3</span><br><span class="line">uint8 UINT16  = 4</span><br><span class="line">uint8 INT32   = 5</span><br><span class="line">uint8 UINT32  = 6</span><br><span class="line">uint8 FLOAT32 = 7</span><br><span class="line">uint8 FLOAT64 = 8</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">string name      <span class="comment"># 字段名称</span></span><br><span class="line">uint32 offset    <span class="comment"># 从点结构体开始的偏移量</span></span><br><span class="line">uint8 datatype   <span class="comment"># 数据类型枚举，见上</span></span><br><span class="line">uint32 count     <span class="comment"># 字段中有多少个元素</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
